<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/styles.css">
    <title>Create your post</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs");%>

    <div class="create_post container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
          <div class="create_user_dev col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">Create Your Post</h1>
            <p class="lead">Blogging is about smart publishing, originating from 'web' and 'log', reaching over 409 million viewers monthly. Content is fire, social media is gasoline; it's a lively form of writing. Starting is key. Posts with images gain 94% more views; companies that blog get 97% more links. Effective blogging is about communication, understanding the unsaid, and building relationships while adding value.</p>
          </div>
        <div class="create_user_user col-lg-6 g-5 py-5">
         <form action="/post_create" method="POST">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="title" class="form-label">Title</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title" name="title" maxlength="60" aria-describedby="titleofpost" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="content" class="form-label">Content</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="content" id="content" maxlength="1000" required>
              <div id="content-limit" class="form-text">Max. : 1000 words</div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
        </form>   
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs");%>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>